jects in Tolkien's work places in Tolkien's work reception of Tolkien medieval scholars scholarship by Tolkien medieval literature stylistic elements themes in Tolkien's works theological/ philosophical concepts and philosophers Tolkien's contemporary history and culture works of literature", 'industryIdentifiers': [{'type': 'ISBN_13', 'identifier': '9780415969420'}, {'type': 'ISBN_10', 'identifier': '0415969425'}], 'readingModes': {'text': False, 'image': True}, 'pageCount': 810, 'printType': 'BOOK', 'categories': ['Fantasy fiction, English'], 'averageRating': 3.5, 'ratingsCount': 3, 'maturityRating': 'NOT_MATURE', 'allowAnonLogging': False, 'contentVersion': '0.1.1.0.preview.1', 'panelizationSummary': {'containsEpubBubbles': False, 'containsImageBubbles': False}, 'imageLinks': {'smallThumbnail': 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=B0loOBA3ejIC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'thumbnail': 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=B0loOBA3ejIC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api'}, 'language': 'en', 'previewLink': 'http://books.google.gr/books?id=B0loOBA3ejIC&pg=PA273&dq=title:the+lay+of+leithian&hl=&cd=4&source=gbs_api', 'infoLink': 'http://books.google.gr/books?id=B0loOBA3ejIC&dq=title:the+lay+of+leithian&hl=&source=gbs_api', 'canonicalVolumeLink': 'https://books.google.com/books/about/J_R_R_Tolkien_Encyclopedia.html?hl=&id=B0loOBA3ejIC'}, 'saleInfo': {'country': 'GR', 'saleability': 'NOT_FOR_SALE', 'isEbook': False}, 'accessInfo': {'country': 'GR', 'viewability': 'PARTIAL', 'embeddable': True, 'publicDomain': False, 'textToSpeechPermission': 'ALLOWED', 'epub': {'isAvailable': False}, 'pdf': {'isAvailable': True, 'acsTokenLink': 'http://books.google.gr/books/download/J_R_R_Tolkien_Encyclopedia-sample-pdf.acsm?id=B0loOBA3ejIC&format=pdf&output=acs4_fulfillment_token&dl_type=sample&source=gbs_api'}, 'webReaderLink': 'http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=B0loOBA3ejIC&hl=&source=gbs_api', 'accessViewStatus': 'S